name: Fish Ahoy!
description:
George Smalley, a local guy with a taste for the fish stick, enjoys one in his home. He is suddenly interrupted by a fish witch, with an evil agenda! 

Mr. Smalley has to traverse several bars in order to please the witch and perhaps on day return to his own self. It is your job to assist him!

Play through the two mini games, while upgrading his abilities on the way, with a captivating story!

All controls are explained during game play.

Playtime is roughly 5-7 minutes. Good luck!
